data.description: Modern Elegance Meets Convenience: A Spectacular 2020-Built Home    Welcome to your dream home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence with a loft, boasting 2653 sq ft of contemporary living space, is a testament to style, comfort, and convenience.  Prime Location:  Nestled in a prime location, this gem is just minutes away from brand-new shopping centers, Kaiser Permanente, and the I-15 freeway. Enjoy the luxury of accessibility without compromising on tranquility.  Outdoor Oasis:  Indulge in the beauty of a low-maintenance pool, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. The water-saving landscape complements the modern design, ensuring an eco-friendly and visually stunning outdoor space. Picture yourself hosting gatherings or unwinding by the poolside after a long day.    Convenience Redefined:  This home goes beyond aesthetics – it offers potential RV parking, providing an additional layer of convenience for those with an adventurous spirit or extra storage needs.    Spacious loft for versatile use, whether it's a home office, play area, or a cozy reading nook.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of style, functionality, and prime location!      Additionally, the third car garage's on the first floor has been transformed into a fifth bedroom. This modification is reversible, allowing you the flexibility to restore it to its original state according to your preferences.
